    "readings, determining accuracy and checking for malfunction. METER TAMPERING: Deliberate interference with the power measuring device in premises, usually for purpose of showing lower or no consumption. MINISTRY OF ENERGY (MOE): is mainly responsible for policy formulation and granting and revoking generation and distribution licenses upon recommendation of the Energy Regulatory Commission (ERC); and settlement of disputes arising from parties aggrieved by ERC’s decision(s). NATIONAL ENERGY POL",
