    "the *977# USSD On your mobile phone, dial *977# and select ‘report incidences’ Select ‘Staff misconduct’ key in their staff number and follow the prompts You can also report corruption/theft on our website kplc ke If you are looking to transfer your account, you need to get in touch with the nearest Kenya Power office However, you will be required to present the following documents; A letter of authority from the previous owner of the account Your national ID Copy of the previous owner’s nation",
