    "nd geothermal.</li><li>They factor in operational costs, inflation, and exchange rate fluctuations.</li><li>They project infrastructure upgrades, like expanding substations or improving rural electrification.</li><li>They then approve rates for different categories of consumers.<br></li></ul><p>The current rates for KPLC tariffs 2025 are outlined in an official electricity tariffs PDF, which you can also find online by Googling “KPLC tariffs 2025 PDF download.”</p><p><strong>Why do tariffs chang",
