    "s The Directorate is also responsible for performing programmed, special and ad hoc technical & performance audits on Rural and County Roads, monitoring and evaluation of special programmes funded by Development Partners as provided in the relevant financial agreements and implementation protocol This will be achieved by evaluating the programming, planning, procurement and the delivery of goods, works and services undertaken by Rural and County Roads to independently verify that funds allocated",
