    "n 6(1), 6(2), a, Programme 19, 20,21,24,25 of KRB Act No 7 of 1999 The Directorate is also established under provisions of the PFM Act 2012; PPAD Act, 2015:theCARA Kenya Roads Board Act,1999 Clause Section 6(1), 6(2), ab, c,g, h, 24,25,26 The Directorate is responsible for preparing, monitoring and evaluating the implementation of the Urban & Park Roads Annual Public Roads Programme, by means of financial, technical and performance audits, the delivery of goods, works and services funded by the",
